                                <p>Indicates that the patient role is a replacement of the supercededId role.</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Fixed value: "REPL" (Replaces) </li>
                                </ul>
                                <p>The typeCode is carried as an attribute of the replacementOf element.</p>
