                        <text>A code to indicate the type of alternative identifier. <p>The Coded with Code System datatype flavour is used to carry this information as follows: </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>The <i>code</i> attribute will contain the value from the vocab stated.<br/>
                                </li>
                                <li>The <i>codeSystem</i> attribute will contain the OID for the vocabulary.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </text>
                    </otherAnnotation>
                </annotations>
